# AI Provider (required for live verification)
# Preferred: Get a free / paid key at https://console.x.ai
# The app supports xAI (Grok vision) natively via OpenAI-compatible SDK.
# Fallback: Standard OpenAI key also works.
XAI_API_KEY=your_xai_api_key_here

# Alternative (if no XAI key):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Note for Treasury evaluators:
# The deployed Vercel URL uses the key configured in Vercel environment variables.
# You do not need a personal key to test the live site.
# For local runs or your own deploy, add your key above.
